Driver class for the opt crawler

Title: OptCrawler

Description: Driver class for the opt crawler. Will create a tree of optimizations, cropping limbs that do not reveal any changes. Will attempt to find the absolute best order in which to run the optimizations.

Copyright: Copyright (c) 2004

Company: Slippery Rock University
